{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"69ec007446","title":"中央关于召开第二次全国组织工作会议的通知","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a619f1838e","index":0,"year":1953,"month":7,"day":null,"articleId":"69ec007446"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"566bf48db9","type":"title","text":"中央关于召开第二次全国组织工作会议的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69ec007446"},{"id":"1ec9347596","type":"paragraph","text":"兹决定于八月二十日以后（具体时间俟中央财经会议结束各地负责同志返回后另通知）召开第二次全国组织工作会议，主要议程为：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69ec007446"},{"id":"1b87c6c4e6","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）关于抽调干部到新建，改建和扩建的重要厂、矿工作的问题；","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69ec007446"},{"id":"ee8185fa5e","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）关于加强对干部的管理问题；","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69ec007446"},{"id":"ef135e2346","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）关于审查干部的问题；","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69ec007446"},{"id":"0285202d82","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）关于整顿党的基层组织和发展新党员的问题。此外，还要研究一下关于干部的培养训练问题。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69ec007446"},{"id":"0d791fe7ac","type":"paragraph","text":"参加会议的人员为：各中央局，各局组织部长，干部处长；各省（市）委组织部长。望根据上述议程搜集材料，准备意见。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69ec007446"}],"page":{"id":"c48b3cbadc","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69ec007446","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}